name: Overgrown (itch) (qwood)
description:
Uh oh! It seems you got locked in... You need to find the exit somewhere in this labyrinth to escape! But look out, a dark force rises in this cold night. Search, but keep an eye on your surroundings, lest you run into the guardian of the labyrinth...

This game was made by a small team of university students for a class over 2 weeks. Featuring custom sprites, enemy AI, and a random map from 3 different presets.
